.TH WL-KBD-CONFIG 1 "April 2026" "wl-kbd-config 0.2"
.SH NAME
wl-kbd-config \- Keyboard layout configuration utility for Wayland window managers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wl-kbd-config
.SH DESCRIPTION
wl-kbd-config is a keyboard layout configuration utility for Wayland window managers. It provides a graphical interface for configuring X keyboard layouts, models, and options.

The application can detect and apply XKB configuration to:
.BR labwc ,
.BR Sway ,
.BR Wayfire ,
.BR River ,
and
.BR Hyprland .
.SH OPTIONS
None. Launch the application to open the settings window.
.SH WINDOW MANAGERS
The application detects the current Wayland session and can apply keyboard layout configuration to:
.TP
.B labwc
Config file: ~/.config/labwc/autostart
.TP
.B Sway
Config file: ~/.config/sway/config
.TP
.B Wayfire
Config file: ~/.config/wayfire.ini
.TP
.B River
Config file: ~/.config/river/init
.TP
.B Hyprland
Config file: ~/.config/hypr/hyprland.conf
.SH BACKUP
Before modifying any WM configuration, the application creates a backup in:
.I ~/.config/wl-kbd-config/backups/
.SH FILES
.I ~/.config/labwc/environment
.RS
labwc XKB configuration file.
.RE
.I ~/.config/wl-kbd-config/backups/
.RS
Directory for configuration backups.
.RE
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wl-kbd (1),
.BR labwc (1),
.BR setxkbmap (1)
.SH AUTHOR
wl-kbd-config is part of the Wayland keyboard layout tooling workspace.
